<html>
  <head>
    <title>Accessibility Statement | Onsko</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Accessibility Statement for Onsko beauty store.">
    <script type="application/jay-headfull" src="../../components/site-header/site-header" names="SiteHeader" contract="../../components/site-header/site-header.jay-contract"></script>
    <script type="application/jay-headfull" src="../../components/site-footer/site-footer" names="SiteFooter" contract="../../components/site-footer/site-footer.jay-contract"></script>
    <script type="application/jay-data">
      data:
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../styles/onsko-theme.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="policy-page-wrapper">
      <jay:SiteHeader />

      <div class="policy-container">
        <h1 class="policy-title">Accessibility Statement</h1>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="policy-heading">Our Commitment</h2>
          <div class="policy-body">
            <p>We are committed to making our website accessible to all users, including those with disabilities. We strive to conform with the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 at the AA level.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="policy-heading">Accessibility Adjustments</h2>
          <div class="policy-body">
            <p>Our website has been adjusted for accessibility in the following ways: clear heading structure and content order; descriptive alt text for images; sufficient color contrast for readability; keyboard-navigable interface; readable font sizes and scalable layouts; accessible form labels and error messages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="policy-heading">Third-Party Content</h2>
          <div class="policy-body">
            <p>While we strive for full accessibility, some third-party content integrated into our website may not fully meet all accessibility standards. We are working with our partners to improve this.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="policy-heading">Contact Us</h2>
          <div class="policy-body">
            <p>If you encounter any accessibility issues or have suggestions for improvement, please contact us at info@mysite.com or call 123-456-7890. We take all feedback seriously and will make every effort to accommodate your needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <jay:SiteFooter />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
